question: give me a list of all conditions diagnosed for patient ece255e8-656b-5e09-8da9-33f88bc270a1
give me a count of all encounters for male patients
query:
PREFIX fhir: <http://hl7.org/fhir/>
PREFIX rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX se: <http://example.org/myontology#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?encounter) AS ?maleEncounterCount)
WHERE {
  ?encounter a fhir:Encounter .
  ?encounter fhir:patient_reference ?patient .
  
  ?patient a fhir:Patient .
  ?patient fhir:gender "male" .
}
